title: Russia’s Invasion of Ukraine, and the Impact on the U.S.
description: Quentin Fottrell, managing editor, personal finance at MarketWatch, discusses Russia's invasion of Ukraine and the impact on the U.S. with Andrew Keshner, MarketWatch tax reporter, and Gregory Robb, senior Washington correspondent.
